messages.messageBody:
Hi! I am driving from Oviedo (near Orlando), FL to visit my mom and sister in Winston-Salem, NC where I grew up. My husband is doing Army reserve training so it'll be me with our three children (7, 5, 2). We'd love to meet unschoolers in the area if anyone has any gatherings planned or would like to meet at a playground, Old Salem (my mom's a tour guide; we could have some fun!), or whatever.

Likewise, if anyone is headed to central Florida, we have lots going on and I can point you in some good directions.

Have a great day!
Jennifer
